The software version listed in the Test Report document at the FCC is "radiolocus-firmware-1.2-wm02.img"
{{FCC ST|06/26/2019}} "XHK_mini5350_V10" and "20180713" are silkscreened on the board in the FCC photos.
There appears to be a USB 2.0 port on the board which may be hidden inside the case.
